## 故障演練三階段對照

| 項目 | 故障前（基線） | 故障中（注入後） | 回復後 |
|---|---|---|---|
| docker.list 存在 | 是 | 否 | yes |
| apt-cache policy 有候選版本 | 是 | 否 | yes |
| docker 重裝可行 | 是 | 否 | yes |
| hello-world 成功 | 是 | N/A | yes |
| nginx curl 成功 | 是 | N/A | yes |

## 手動修復 vs Snapshot 回復

| 面向 | 手動修復 | Snapshot 回復 |
|---|---|---|
| 所需時間 | 30min - 1 hour | 1-5min (just started to use it) |
| 適用情境 | when you know the problem | its like a checkpoint when you messed up something and too lazy to find the problem |
| 風險 | potential human error especially beginner | nothing since its a checkpoint |

## Snapshot 保留策略
- 新增條件：adding more things to the system before changing it 100%
- 保留上限：depending on the disk size since i only got 25 gb probably 1-5 snapshot
- 刪除條件：delete snapshot when you feel like its not useful anymore, since you upgraded

## 最小可重現命令鏈
（列出讓他人能重現故障注入與回復驗證的命令序列）
# 1. Check baseline
ls /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list
apt-cache policy docker-ce
sudo docker run hello-world
sudo docker run -d -p 8080:80 nginx
curl localhost:8080

# 2. Inject failure
sudo rm /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list

# 3. Verify failure
ls /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list
apt-cache policy docker-ce
sudo docker run hello-world    # should fail
sudo docker run -d -p 8080:80 nginx   # should fail
curl localhost:8080           # should fail

# 4. Recover using snapshot
# (In VMware GUI) Revert VM to snapshot 'docker-ready'

# 5. Verify recovery
ls /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list
apt-cache policy docker-ce
sudo docker run hello-world    # should succeed
sudo docker run -d -p 8080:80 nginx
curl localhost:8080

